text: Nankana Sahib District or Khairpur Bhattian () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Nankana Sahib is the capital. ==Administration== Nankana Sahib District is administratively subdivided into four tehsils: * Nankana Sahib Tehsil * Safdarabad Tehsil * Sangla Hill Tehsil * Shahkot Tehsil Category:Lahore Division
title: Nankana Sahib District
